Given the following program and the first line of a loop, optimize it out via loop unrolling.. The program is int g;
int main() {
  short ak[8];
  unsigned p2;
  unsigned short p3 = 4294967289L;
  unsigned p4;
  for (p2 = 0; p2 <= 7; p2 += 1)
    for (p4 = 0; p4 <= 7; p4 += 1)
      if (g < 0)
        for (p4 = 0; p4 <= 7; p4 += 1)
          if (ak[p3])
            break;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is if (ak[p3]).
